    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just exhausting. the idea of \"letting go\" sounds nice but it feels so impossible to actually do while you're still stuck in this body, feeling all this weight. like, if it's really just a \"glitch\" or something pointless, why does it have to be so painful to just stop? what does \"letting go\" actually look like if you really want that peace?",
